Recommends: libproj0
Description: Geo-Spatial Data Viewer
 It is a lightweight viewer for geo-spatial data and products written in
 Python and Qt4.
 .
 GSDView is modular and has a simple plug-in architecture.
 .
 It is mainly intended to be a graphical front-end for the GDAL library
 and tools.
 .
